            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/michael_chertoff_343124",
        "quote": "Well, I think first of all there was a failure to have real, clear information at our disposal. There was a real lack of situational awareness. We didn't have the capabilities on the ground to give us real-time, accurate assessments of the physical condition of the city.",
