    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/michael_chertoff_343131",
        "quote": "The second is there are some communities that we thought originally would take mobile homes that have decided they don't want them. And we're not going to cram mobile homes down the throats of communities in Louisiana and the Gulf - and other parts of the Gulf Coast.",
